name: Stardom #0001
description:
Stardom collection is an early study for the artist’s project that results in generative drawing of gem stones. In this collection, a circle (not depicted) is divided into triangles and other geometric shapes to form stars with varying number of points. Each piece consists of hundreds of semi-transparent triangles that set the color mood and dozens of triangles on top providing the shading/highlights and the white outlines (in some sets not shown for more artistic look). 

Dimensions: 4800 x 4800
